data.description: Rarely does an opportunity like this present itself to acquire the perfect stylish residence in this crazy market...you'll want to pay particular attention to this one! Magnificently presented ranch which has been precisely re-constructed to offer the ideal one floor living space designed for easy living and entertaining. Sprawling brand new kitchen boasts abundant new cabinetry, granite counters accented backsplash, stainless steel appliances, bar area and flanked by dining accented with shipped lapped wall. Spacious living room w/fireplace, generous foyer area and convenience of first floor laundry. Master suite is accented with private bath and sliding barn door. Full waterproofed sprawling basement, 2 car attached garage and relaxing covered back patio overlooking the perfect sized back yard. Updates Include: New, New, New Roof, Soffit, Siding, Windows, All New Drywall, Insulation, Exterior Doors, Electrical Panel, Electric, Plumbing, Trendy Lighting, HWT, New Kitchen Cabinets, Granite, Appliances, All New Flooring and More! With schools, shops, dining & leisure facilities within easy reach, this is the ideal place to call home. Be prepared for this to be 'love at first sight'.
